parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the air conditioner compressor can cause the air conditioner to stop working, leading to discomfort and potential health risks, especially in hot weather. or stops working altogether. In some cases
causing the engine to stall or the power steering to fail.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Metal Shards in the Air Conditioner System
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The presence of metal shards in the air conditioner system can cause the system to fail, leading to discomfort and potential health risks, especially in hot weather. In some cases, the shards can also cause damage to other components, leading to costly repairs.
symptoms: The air conditioner blows hot air
or stops working altogether. In some cases
causing the engine to stall or the power steering to fail.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Lack of Recall or Warranty Coverage
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The lack of recall or warranty coverage for the air conditioner compressor failure can cause financial burden to the vehicle owners, who may have to pay for costly repairs out of pocket.
symptoms: Vehicle owners are not notified of the potential problem
and are not offered any assistance or compensation for repairs.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the airbag to deploy in a crash can lead to serious injuries or fatalities.
symptoms: Airbags do not deploy in a crash

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The random deployment of an airbag can cause loss of control, accidents, and injuries.
The inability to obtain a recall repair can leave the vehicle in an unsafe condition, increasing the risk of injuries or fatalities.
The illumination of the SRS light can indicate a problem with the airbag system, which can lead to airbag failure in a crash.
The Takata airbag recall issues can lead to airbag failure, injuries, or fatalities.
symptoms: Receipt of Takata airbag recall notice
